{"tid":1034713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑老鼠藥毒殺23歲子 將軍澳善明邨精神病婦涉謀殺被捕","createTime":"2019-02-24T06:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T07:56:34.000Z","uid":13468,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"685005d7ded3490299647516bd3c662fa0fe3289","tid":1034713,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T06:33:29.000Z","msg":"疑老鼠藥毒殺23歲子 將軍澳善明邨精神病婦涉謀殺被捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳調景嶺善明邨，昨晚發生懷疑謀殺及企圖自殺倫常命案，案中一名23歲黎姓男子死亡，其55歲疑有精神問題的趙姓母親送院救治，她涉嫌謀殺被捕。警方將於稍後交代案情。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，疑有精神病的趙婦有死念，但擔心健康狀況良好的兒子乏人照顧，遂以老鼠藥毒殺兒子，趙婦亦服了小量，故只是感到不適。<br />\n<br />\n現場為善明邨善禮樓，保安員昨晚10時29分報案，消防接報後到場破門入內，發現屋內一名23歲男子已當場死亡。西貢區區議員方國珊早上到場了解事件，指趙婦昨晚到大堂向當值保安員求助，指其黎姓兒子在寓所內暈倒，而趙婦求助時的神智亦迷糊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1440594/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1440594%2F&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=d5ecf84d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1440594%2F&h=e0778e33\" target=\"_blank\">hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1440594/</a>"},{"pid":"45a3dc889d8a0963a90fd571aa478489209559a7","tid":1034713,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T06:35:18.000Z","msg":"d字眼咁似之前見過"},{"pid":"ff6f413448fda3857d064ba3b06e15c0c2d90238","tid":1034713,"uid":40867,"like":54,"dislike":3,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"支持人道毀滅所有精神病"},{"pid":"44b0349c94c5a09ecaa7d6af472cd83a26359a9d","tid":1034713,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T06:37:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1440594/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1440594%2F&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=d5ecf84d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealti